help_center_faqs.question: How do I locate my transaction ID?
help_center_faqs.answer: Find your transaction ID in the purchase confirmation email or in your accounts 'Billing History' section.

help_center_faqs.question: How long does it take to learn the app?
help_center_faqs.answer: Learning the app depends on your familiarity with similar tools. Most users get comfortable within a few hours, with full proficiency achievable in about a week of regular use.

help_center_faqs.question: How does the affiliate program work?
help_center_faqs.answer: Our affiliate program lets you earn commissions by referring new users. Sign up, share your unique link, and earn a percentage of each sale made through your referrals.

help_center_faqs.question: Do licenses expire?
help_center_faqs.answer: Licenses typically do not expire, allowing lifelong use for the purchased item under the license terms, unless otherwise specified.

help_center_faqs.question: What are common issues with PayPal, Skrill, or credit card payments?
help_center_faqs.answer: Common issues include declined cards, incorrect details, or payment gateway errors. Verify your information, ensure sufficient funds, or contact support for help.

help_center_faqs.question: Do authors respond to requests outside of support?
help_center_faqs.answer: Authors are not obligated to respond to requests outside the support scope, but some may assist at their discretion. Contact them via the items page.

help_center_faqs.question: What if I forget my username or password?
help_center_faqs.answer: Click 'Forgot Password' on the login page to reset your password via email. If you forgot your username, contact support with your registered email address.

help_center_faqs.question: Do I need a Regular or Extended License?
help_center_faqs.answer: Choose a Regular License for a single end product with limited distribution. Opt for an Extended License for multiple end products or broader commercial use.

help_center_faqs.question: Are free tutorials available?
help_center_faqs.answer: Yes, we provide free tutorials on our website and YouTube channel, covering basics to advanced features to help you get started.

help_center_faqs.question: How do I download purchased items?
help_center_faqs.answer: After purchase, go to your account dashboard, navigate to 'My Purchases,' and click the download link next to your item. Ensure you're logged in.

help_center_faqs.question: Why do prepaid credits expire?
help_center_faqs.answer: Prepaid credits expire to encourage timely use and maintain system efficiency. Check the terms for specific expiration periods.

help_center_faqs.question: What if the author hasnt responded to my request?
help_center_faqs.answer: If an author doesnt respond within a reasonable time, contact our support team for assistance or to escalate the issue.

help_center_faqs.question: How do I contact an author?
help_center_faqs.answer: Go to the items page, click the authors profile, and use the 'Contact Author' form to send a message.

help_center_faqs.question: How do I extend or renew item support?
help_center_faqs.answer: Visit your accounts 'My Purchases,' find the item, and select the option to extend or renew support if available.

help_center_faqs.question: Is there a 14-day trial available?
help_center_faqs.answer: Yes, we offer a 14-day trial for new users. You can explore all features during this period without any commitment. Sign up on our website to start your trial.

help_center_faqs.question: How easy is it to change a license type?
help_center_faqs.answer: To change a license type, purchase the new license for the item. Contact support for assistance or to discuss upgrade options.

help_center_faqs.question: What are the benefits of a Premium Membership?
help_center_faqs.answer: Premium Membership includes unlimited access to all features, priority support, exclusive content, and regular updates to enhance your experience.

help_center_faqs.question: What does item support include?
help_center_faqs.answer: Item support includes help with installation, basic usage, and bug fixes from the author, typically for a set period after purchase.

help_center_faqs.question: What is the policy for removing ratings or reviews?
help_center_faqs.answer: Ratings or reviews can be removed if they violate our guidelines, such as containing inappropriate content. Contact support to request a review.

help_center_faqs.question: Can I use the same item for multiple end products?
help_center_faqs.answer: For multiple end products, youll need an Extended License. A Regular License limits use to a single end product.

help_center_faqs.question: How can I view and download invoices?
help_center_faqs.answer: Log into your account, go to 'Billing History,' and select the transaction to view or download your invoice as a PDF.

help_center_faqs.question: What are PayPal disputes and chargebacks?
help_center_faqs.answer: Disputes occur when a buyer contests a transaction with PayPal. Chargebacks happen when a cardholder disputes a charge via their bank. Contact support to resolve these issues.

help_center_faqs.question: Whats the difference between supported and unsupported items?
help_center_faqs.answer: Supported items include author assistance for a set period, while unsupported items do not. Check the items page for support details before purchase.

help_center_faqs.question: How do licenses work for purchased items?
help_center_faqs.answer: Licenses define how you can use purchased items. A Regular License covers single end products for personal or commercial use, while an Extended License allows multiple end products or broader usage.

help_center_faqs.question: Why is there a $20 minimum for prepaid credits?
help_center_faqs.answer: The $20 minimum ensures cost-effective transactions and aligns with our pricing structure for prepaid credits.

help_center_faqs.question: How do I contact an author?
help_center_faqs.answer: Visit the items page, click on the authors profile, and use the 'Contact Author' form to send a message directly.

help_center_faqs.question: How do I save my credit card details?
help_center_faqs.answer: During checkout, select the option to save your card details for future purchases. You can manage saved cards in your account settings.

help_center_faqs.question: Is there a month-to-month payment option?
help_center_faqs.answer: Yes, we offer a flexible month-to-month payment plan alongside annual subscriptions. You can choose the option that suits you best during signup.

help_center_faqs.question: Where can I find my license code?
help_center_faqs.answer: Your license code is in your purchase confirmation email or under 'My Purchases' in your account dashboard.
